            "reviews": "“Unashamedly similar to One Finger Death Punch where you punch dudes to the beat, but... You can upload and battle through your own music!”<br><a href=\"https://www.pcgamer.com/terrorhythm-is-a-rhythm-brawler-game-with-extra-rhythm/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >PC Gamer</a><br><br>“This game that is born highly addictive exhilaration by combining rhythmic action and stylish attack animation to the ease of playing. People who like sound games definitely should play this one.”<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.4gamer.net/games/282/G028219/20180416002/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >4Gamer•net</a><br><br>“Addictive, good control response, great music and graphics. It is an enjoyable game to anyone who enjoys rhythm and fast-paced beat ‘em up games, whether they are a casual or a hardcore player.”<br>9/10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://3rd-strike.com/terrorhythm-trrt-preview/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >3rd-strike</a><br>",
